                     <interp inst="t17770409-44-off214" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing two bushels and an half of oats, value 5 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17770409-44-victim414" type="victimName">
                     Charles
                      Laycock
                  <interp inst="t17770409-44-victim414" type="surname" value="Laycock"></interp>
